## ⚖️ License / Legal Notice

You are legally allowed to host Unity projects on GitHub, including AR Foundation-based projects, **as long as**:

- You **don’t include Unity binaries or proprietary packages** (`*.dll`, `libiPhone-lib.a`, etc.).
- You **don’t distribute the Unity Editor or licensed components** directly.
- Your usage follows the [Unity Terms of Service](https://unity.com/legal/terms-of-service/software)

This repo adheres to those conditions by excluding platform binaries using `.gitignore`.

---

## 🛠 Future Setup Tips

- Want to build for Android? Install the **ARCore XR Plugin**.
- Using AR Session Origin or AR Raycast? Check Unity's [AR Foundation Samples](https://github.com/Unity-Technologies/arfoundation-samples).

